	<title>registry: compute checksum on upload of an image1.5.0</title>
	<description>
		<paragraph id="1">
			<sentence id="1.1">To avoid the issue where imported image layers may have a different checksum when they are exported we should compute the layer checksum while uploading it and using that computed checksum in a second request to complete it (https://github.com/docker/distribution/blob/master/doc/SPEC.md#completed-upload)</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="2">
			<sentence id="2.1">related to https://github.com/docker/distribution/issues/112</sentence>
		</paragraph>
	</description>
</bug>
